  .notes Well, maybe there is a big idea after all.
  .notes (I'm hesitant to mention this because it's not well established and, anyway, you should find your own big idea. But ...)
  .notes Through social interaction you are able to rediscover what is in some sense already encoded in your core knowledge.
  .notes That, anyway, is one idea about how humans come to know about objects, causes, minds and the rest.


